    public class FormEntryComponent
extends com.i2rd.componentfactory.component.ComponentFactoryComponent<com.i2rd.componentfactory.mediator.ComponentFactoryMediator>
    Main component for form entry. Pass in a FormControllerConfig to the constructor. You can listen for ActionEvents on form "submit" or "save & exit". This object initializes the form UI during init().
    Author:
    Jonathan Crosmer (jcrosmer@i2rd.com)
